        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;THE GEEZERS - EXPECT DELAYS┬Ā- Back by popular demand Buckle up and take an uproarious ride with the Geezers, Sid Filkow and Patrick Cassidy as the reprise their October show and navigate the blind curves and pot-holes of Island life, and life in general. The October performances were sold out so get your tickets pronto. [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
