    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;&nbsp; Come laugh and be wowed by three of Canada\\'s best magicians! East Van legend Travis Bernhardt, who comedian Dino Archie called, &quot;the hardest guy to follow in Vancouver,&quot; has toured his award-winning magic shows and improv comedy shows across Canada since 2008. He also consults for film and TV, most recently Disney\\'s Descendants: Wicked [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
