        "@value": "SS Forum &#8211; Michael Barnett &#8211; The US and the Middle East: What Now?"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;&nbsp; As global news shifts daily itŌĆÖs easy to feel adrift. Professor Michael Barnett of George Washington University, can help us identify the realities under the headlines. Whether you follow international politics closely or simply want clarity in an uncertain time, this is a rare chance to speak with an expert who sees the deeper [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
      }
    ],
