      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tParallel Art Show (PAS)\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tSeptember 27, 2025 @ 10:00 am - October 18, 2025 @ 4:00 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\nThe Salt Spring National Art Prize (SSNAP) is a biennial, juried competition and exhibition of Canadian contemporary art. Held on Salt Spring Island, BC, SSNAP celebrates and promotes artists from across the country through a major exhibition, significant awards, and national recognition.\nThe Parallel Art Show (PAS) is a juried exhibition showcasing artists from the Southern Gulf Islands, presented alongside the Salt Spring National Art Prize. Featuring a diverse range of local talent, PAS highlights innovative contemporary work across disciplines and runs concurrently with SSNAP at ArtSpring.┬Ā\nOpening Gala for PAS ŌĆō 6-8pm Sept 28 (*No Tickets)\nPas Exhibition in ArtSpring Gallery ŌĆō Sept 27 ŌĆō Oct 19, 2025\nClosing gala awards night for SSNAP + PAS ŌĆō 6-9pm Oct 18 (*Tickets required. On Sale Now!)\nPAS Artists:\n\nMatt Adolf ŌĆó David Allan ŌĆó Seth Berkowitz ŌĆó Chintan Bolliger\nCarole Bondaroff ŌĆó Sally Born ŌĆó Joan Carrigan ŌĆó Leo Chan ŌĆó Gary Cherneff\nStefanie Denz ŌĆó Kyle Durant ŌĆó Mimi Fujino ŌĆó Dina Gonz├Īlez Mascar├│\nDiana Hayes ŌĆó Martin Herbert ŌĆó Jen Holmes ŌĆó Elisabeth Jahren\nDavid James ŌĆó John David James ŌĆó Cathryn Jenkins ŌĆó Amy Jones\nGarry Kaye ŌĆó Laura Keil ŌĆó Kasumi Lampitoc ŌĆó Bob Leatherbarrow\nCheryl Long ŌĆó Jennifer Maksymetz ŌĆó Gillian McConnell\nLarry Melious ŌĆó Chris Metze ŌĆó Robert Moss ŌĆó Doreen Palme\nPatricia Parkes ŌĆó Max Parsons ŌĆó Elaine Potter ŌĆó Matt Robertson\n\n\nLexane Rousseau ŌĆó Andrea Russell ŌĆó Anette Schrage ŌĆó Katherine Scott\nKaren Selk ŌĆó Sandy Shreve ŌĆó Jeannette Sirois ŌĆó Nathalie St-Amant\nAlicja Swiatlon ŌĆó Anna Szul ŌĆó Melanie Thompson ŌĆó Ida Marie Threadkell\nSherry Williams ŌĆó April Winter ŌĆó Margo Zak\n\n┬Ā\nPAS JURY\n┬ĀSteven McNeil ŌĆō Chief Curator & Director of Collections and Exhibitions, Art Gallery of Greater Victoria\nKim Pollard ŌĆō Artist, curator, consultant, gallerist, and mentor based on Pender Island\nAlexandra Montgomery ŌĆō Former Director/CEO of the Bill Reid Gallery and Gardiner Museum, now based on Salt Spring Island\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tStart:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t September 27, 2025 @ 10:00 am \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEnd:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t October 18, 2025 @ 4:00 pm \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: Gallery Exhibits & Events\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t saltspringartprize.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tSSNAP\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tPhone\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t250-931-1141\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEmail\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tinfo@saltspringartprize.ca\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tView Organizer Website\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Gallery \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tPhone\n\t\t\t\t\t 250.537.2102 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tAdd to calendar\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tGoogle Calendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tiCalendar\t\n\n\t\t\t