        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Fri Jan 23, 7:30pm | Winners of a Juno Award and global fans alike, CanadaŌĆÖs genre-defying string quartet The Fretless is reshaping the way audiences hear traditional music. Rooted in [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
