        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tMICHAEL KAESHAMMER\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tMarch 19, 2026 @ 7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$10 ŌĆō $42\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThu Mar 19, 7:30pm | HeŌĆÖs back! Beloved by ArtSpring audiences and celebrated worldwide, Michael Kaeshammer is a virtuosic pianist, charismatic performer, and master showman. His concerts are high-octane journeys through jazz, boogie-woogie, pop, and soulŌĆöinfused with signature charm, playful improvisation, and unstoppable joy. Whether heŌĆÖs lighting up the keys in a driving rhythm or crooning a tender ballad, Kaeshammer brings audiences to their feet with musical storytelling thatŌĆÖs both dazzling and deeply personal. A seven-time JUNO nominee and internationally touring artist, Kaeshammer delivers a world-class concert experience thatŌĆÖs spontaneous, heartfelt, and unforgettable. ŌĆ£He doesnŌĆÖt just play the pianoŌĆöhe performs magic,ŌĆØ says one fan. Come see why this genre-defying artist has become a Salt Spring favourite.\nBUY TICKETS\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t March 19, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 ŌĆō $42 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: ArtSpring Presents 2025-26\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tPhone\n\t\t\t\t\t 250.537.2102 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tAdd to calendar\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tGoogle Calendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tiCalendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook 365\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook Live\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t March 19, 2026 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 ŌĆō $42 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: ArtSpring Presents 2025-26\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tPhone\n\t\t\t\t\t 250.537.2102 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\n\t\n    \n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Navigation\n\t\t\n\t\t\t┬½ OSTARA PROJECT: Roots & Wings Concert\n\t\t\tMAKANA YOUTH CHOIRS: Spring Term ┬╗\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t"
