        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Mar 13 | Mar 14 | IMMERSIVE EXPERIENCE: A WEEKLONG RESIDENCY INCLUDING FILM SCREENING &amp; CONCERT Only 5 percent of jazz instrumentalists are women. Ostara Project is looking to change [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
