    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tMET OPERA NOW ON SALE: La Sonnambula (AP)\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tOctober 18, 2025 @ 10:00 am - 1:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$15 ŌĆō $25\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSIX OPERAS NOW ON SALE | First up ŌĆö Sat Oct. 18 10am | Following triumphant Live in HD┬Āperformances in GounodŌĆÖs┬ĀRom├®o┬Āet┬ĀJuliette, VerdiŌĆÖs┬ĀLa┬ĀTraviata, and DonizettiŌĆÖs┬ĀLucia┬Ādi┬ĀLammermoor, Nadine Sierra summits another peak of the soprano repertoire as Amina, who sleepwalks her way into audiencesŌĆÖ hearts in BelliniŌĆÖs poignant tale of love lost and found. In his new production, Rolando Villaz├│nŌĆöthe tenor who has embarked on a brilliant second career as a directorŌĆöretains the operaŌĆÖs original setting in the Swiss Alps but uses its somnambulant plot to explore the emotional and psychological valleys of the mind. Tenor Xabier Anduaga co-stars as AminaŌĆÖs fianc├®, Elvino, alongside soprano Sydney Mancasola as her rival, Lisa, and bass Alexander Vinogradov as Count Rodolfo. Riccardo Frizza takes the podium for one of operaŌĆÖs most ravishing works.\n3:15 hours with intermission | Sung in Italian | NEW PRODUCTION\nBUY TICKETS\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t October 18, 2025 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t10:00 am - 1:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $15 ŌĆō $25 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Categories: ArtSpring Presents 2025-26, Metropolitan Opera\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t artspring.ca \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tArtSpring\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \