        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;&nbsp; The Unseen Island is an ambitious exhibition of new work by three Salt Spring Island artists, Eli Horn, James K-M and Denise Okan, September 5 - 21, 2025. Opening [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
