        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;A vibrant and diverse showcase by local Indigenous and M├®tis artists, featuring traditional and contemporary expressions. Explore intricate beadwork in the M├®tis floral style, eco art prints made from natural [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
