        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Free Daily May 18-June 1 | 10am-4pm | This May, coinciding with Salt SpringŌĆÖs own legendary Canadian artist, educator, and conservationist Robert BatemanŌĆÖs 95th birthday, comes an extraordinary never-before-seen exhibition [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
