    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tLand & Lineage\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tJuly 4, 2025 @ 7:00 pm - 8:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$10 ŌĆō $25\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\nLand & Lineage: A Ceremony of Belonging\nThe Imaginelle Mystery School and Naomi Jason present Land & Lineage: An Embodied Ceremony of Belonging. A series of solo prayerformances by local Salt Spring women, showcasing NaomiŌĆÖs work as a dancer, choreographer, community mentor and ceremonialist.\nLand & Lineage is an invitation to tune into the roots of our lineages and the lived connection to the land across time. We dance as an offering of allyship to the stewards of these territories. We dance for the repair and reclamation of our own ancestral wounds and gifts. We dance as a ceremony of reconciliation with what has been. We hold a prayer for wholeness, integrity and peace and a commitment to show up more fully for this land that we live on. We hold this prayer as a rite of passage into deeper leadership within our communities.\nWith Q&A\nBUY TICKETS\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t July 4, 2025 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:00 pm - 8:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 ŌĆō $25 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t naomijason.com \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tImaginelle Mystery School\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEmail\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tignite@naomijason.com\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tPhone\n\t\t\t\t\t 250.537.2102 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tAdd to calendar\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tGoogle Calendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tiCalendar\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook 365\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\tOutlook Live\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t July 4, 2025 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:00 pm - 8:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $10 ŌĆō $25 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t naomijason.com \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tImaginelle Mystery School\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEmail\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tignite@naomijason.com\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tPhone\n\t\t\t\t\t 250.537.2102 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\n\t\n    \n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Navigation\n\t\t\n\t\t\t┬½ Ser