        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;THU FEB 13 | 7:30pm | Dave BrubeckŌĆÖs enduring 1959 album ŌĆ£Time OutŌĆØ is an American sonic masterpiece and resonates to this day. The shifting time changes and melodic and [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
