        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;&nbsp; Nov 26, 5-7pm | Led by artist facilitator Shannon Litzenberger (performing World After Dark on Saturday, November 23) and creative contributor Marie-Jos├®e Chartier, this workshop will explore embodied practice, [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
