        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Fridays, Sep 13-Nov 24 |The Makana Choirs are the place to develop healthy singing habits, learn musical literary skills, and put on a concert. All while having fun with friends! [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
