        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t \n\n                 \t\n\n\n\t ┬½ All Events\n\n\t\n\tThis event has passed.\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\tVetta Chamber Music Presents: Liminal Spaces (Concert 1 of 5)\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tSeptember 30, 2024 @ 2:30 pm - 4:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t-\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$25 ŌĆō $30\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\nConcert 1┬Ā| Liminal Spaces\nW A Mozart | String Quartet No. 19 in C major, K. 465, ŌĆ£DissonnanceŌĆØ\nJeffrey Ryan | String Quartet #4: Inspirare\nL. van Beethoven | String Quartet No. 10 in e-flast major, Op. 74 ŌĆ£HarpŌĆØ\nJoan Blackman violin\nMaria Larinoff, violin\nDavid Harding, viola\nZoltan Rozsnyai, cello\nMusic, as in life, moves between in and out breath, between excitement and calm. This program explores the movement between these two interconnected forces and that moment of transition when the swing is suspended in mid-air, the liminal space.\nConsider purchasing all five concerts for a package price of $125 ($25/concert.)\nBUY TICKETS CONCERT 1\nBUY TICKETS CONCERT 2 (Nov 18)\nBUY TICKETS CONCERT 3 (Jan 27)\nBUY TICKETS CONCERT 4 (Mar 10)\nBUY TICKETS CONCERT 5 (May 5)\n┬Ā\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t September 30, 2024 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2:30 pm - 4:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $25 ŌĆō $30 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: Rental\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWebsite:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t vettamusic.com \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tVetta\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t ArtSpring ŌĆō Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n100 Jackson Avenue\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSalt Spring Island,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV8K 2V8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t