        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Fri Aug 23, 4pm | Join our artist in residence, pianist and soprano Rachel Fenlon, for an intimate reveal of her upcoming seasonŌĆÖs repertoire, a sample of her work, how [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
