        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Opening Reception: August 22 | 5:00-7:30pm For 24 years, Photosynthesis Group has exhibited its photographic interpretations, becoming the longest continuous photography show on Salt Spring. Collaborating with ArtSpring since 2001, [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
